(2364, 1, 'Jesus in the Wilderness with the Devil', '<p>Matthew 4 and Luke 4 contain the record of God leading Jesus into the Judean Wilderness to be tempted by the Devil. Jesus&rsquo; temptation was a necessity in order for him to be tempted in all ways like other humans are, and it also set the stage for the conflict between Jesus and the Devil. In the temptation, we learn things about the Devil and his power, and why it is that evil people seem to always get to the top of politics, art, music, religion, education, and more.</p> <p>Verses: Deut. 6:13; 8:1-3; Matt. 4:1-11; 12:31-32; Luke 4:1-13</p> <p>Teacher: John Schoenheit</p>', '2023-02-07', 'SpiritAndTruth_VF', 0, '35:32', 0, 0, null, 'NBtMjjjOWjA', null, 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/NBtMjjjOWjA/mqdefault.jpg', 1, 1, null, 1, 5, null),
(2365, 1, 'The Peace that Passes Understanding', '<p>This teaching explores the topic of &ldquo;peace&rdquo; by highlighting what the Old Testament says about peace, what Jesus said about peace, and what the Church Epistles say about peace. In the process, the Bible reveals what things are associated with peace, how one develops peace, and the benefits of peace.</p> <p>Verses: Psalm 119:165; Isa. 9:1-7; 26:3; Luke 12:22-31; John 14:27; 16:33; Rom. 14:15, 17, 19; Col. 3:15; Phil. 4:4-9</p> <p>Teacher: Sue Carlson</p>', '2023-02-12', 'SpiritAndTruth_VF', 0, '34:40', 0, 0, null, 'VRU7C5q2p-Q', null, 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VRU7C5q2p-Q/mqdefault.jpg', 1, 1, null, 1, 0, null),
